{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775889027538,"sessionID":"ses_284c439adffe9RjKJYXKdSj8yG","part":{"id":"prt_d7b3c06840012Hvru0QyupNPP6","messageID":"msg_d7b3be32a001DA2dvSOi948F21","sessionID":"ses_284c439adffe9RjKJYXKdSj8yG","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-af9a6a6b554f4a4e89e401ac6338ebdd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Specification: AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端\n2: \n3: **Module:** sdk-python  \n4: **Language:** Python  \n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: 为 AgentCube Python SDK 实现统一的 HTTP 客户端基础设施，支持控制面和数据面的 HTTP 通信，包括连接池管理、超时配置、会话管理和错误处理。\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Requirements\n16: \n17: ### Requirement: HTTP Session 创建与连接池\n18: \n19: 系统应使用 `requests.Session` 配合 `HTTPAdapter` 实现连接池复用，支持自定义连接池大小。\n20: \n21: #### Scenario: 默认连接池配置\n22: \n23: - **GIVEN** 调用 `create_session()` 不传入参数\n24: - **WHEN** 创建 HTTP session\n25: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 为 `http://` 和 `https://` 两个 scheme 各挂载一个 `HTTPAdapter`，连接池参数为 `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: 自定义连接池配置\n28: \n29: - **GIVEN** 调用 `create_session(pool_connections=20, pool_maxsize=30)`\n30: - **WHEN** 创建 HTTP session\n31: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 使用指定的参数创建 `HTTPAdapter` 并挂载到两个 scheme\n32: \n33: #### Scenario: Session 返回类型\n34: \n35: - **GIVEN** `create_session()` 被调用\n36: - **WHEN** 函数返回\n37: - **THEN** 返回值 SHALL 是 `requests.Session` 实例\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ### Requirement: Control Plane HTTP 客户端\n42: \n43: 系统应实现 `ControlPlaneClient` 支持 Workload Manager 的会话管理 API。\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: 创建会话请求\n46: \n47: - **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` 实例已初始化，且有有效的 `auth_token`\n48: - **WHEN** 调用 `create_session(name=\"test\", namespace=\"default\", ttl=3600)`\n49: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 发送 `POST {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` 请求，包含：\n50:   - Header `Content-Type: application/json`\n51:   - Header `Authorization: Bearer {token}`\n52:   - JSON body `{\"name\": \"test\", \"namespace\": \"default\", \"ttl\": 3600, \"metadata\": null}`\n53:   - 超时 `(connect_timeout, timeout)` 默认 `(5.0, 120)`\n54: - **AND** 返回响应中的 `data[\"sessionId\"]`\n55: - **AND** 若响应缺少 `sessionId` 则抛出 `ValueError`\n56: \n57: #### Scenario: 创建会话带 metadata\n58: \n59: - **GIVEN** 调用 `create_session(name=\"test\", namespace=\"default\", metadata={\"key\": \"value\"}, ttl=3600)`\n60: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n61: - **THEN** JSON body SHALL 包含 `metadata: {\"key\": \"value\"}`\n62: \n63: #### Scenario: 删除会话 - 成功\n64: \n65: - **GIVEN** `session_id` 存在且有效\n66: - **WHEN** 调用 `delete_session(session_id)`\n67: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 发送 `DELETE {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}`\n68: - **AND** 返回 `True`\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: 删除会话 - 404 视为成功\n71: \n72: - **GIVEN** `session_id` 不存在\n73: - **WHEN** 服务端返回 404\n74: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 返回 `True`（而非抛出异常）\n75: \n76: #### Scenario: 删除会话 - 其他错误\n77: \n78: - **GIVEN** 服务端返回非 2xx/404 错误\n79: - **WHEN** `delete_session` 执行\n80: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 记录警告日志\n81: - **AND** 返回 `False`\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Workload Manager URL 解析\n84: \n85: - **GIVEN** 构造函数未传入 `workload_manager_url`\n86: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n87: - **THEN** `base_url` SHALL 从环境变量 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 获取\n88: \n89: #### Scenario: Workload Manager URL 显式传入\n90: \n91: - **GIVEN** 构造函数传入 `workload_manager_url=\"https://wm.example.com\"`\n92: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n93: - **THEN** `base_url` SHALL 使用传入的值\n94: \n95: #### Scenario: Auth Token 解析 - 参数优先\n96: \n97: - **GIVEN** 构造函数传入 `auth_token=\"my-token\"`\n98: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n99: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 使用传入的 token，设置默认 header `Authorization: Bearer my-token`\n100: \n101: #### Scenario: Auth Token 解析 - 从文件读取\n102: \n103: - **GIVEN** 构造函数未传入 `auth_token`\n104: - **AND** 文件 `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` 存在且包含 `sa-token`\n105: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n106: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 调用 `read_token_from_file` 读取 token\n107: - **AND** 设置默认 header `Authorization: Bearer sa-token`\n108: \n109: #### Scenario: Auth Token 为空 - 无 Authorization header\n110: \n111: - **GIVEN** 构造函数未传入 `auth_token`\n112: - **AND** token 文件不存在或为空\n113: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n114: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL NOT 设置 `Authorization` header\n115: \n116: #### Scenario: Close 方法\n117: \n118: - **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` 有活跃的 HTTP session\n119: - **WHEN** 调用 `client.close()`\n120: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 关闭底层的 `requests.Session`\n121: \n122: ---\n123: \n124: ### Requirement: Code Interpreter Data Plane HTTP 客户端\n125: \n126: 系统应实现 `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 支持 Router 代理的代码执行和文件操作 API。\n127: \n128: #### Scenario: Base URL 构建 - 从参数\n129: \n130: - **GIVEN** 构造时传入 `base_url=\"https://router.example.com/path/\"`\n131: - **WHEN** 初始化客户端\n132: - **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL 直接使用传入的 `base_url`\n133: \n134: #### Scenario: Base URL 构建 - 从 router_url 和 cr_name\n135: \n136: - **GIVEN** 构造时传入 `router_url=\"https://router.example.com\"`, `namespace=\"prod\"`, `cr_name=\"my-interpreter\"`\n137: - **AND** 未传入 `base_url`\n138: - **WHEN** 初始化客户端\n139: - **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL 为 `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/prod/code-interpreters/my-interpreter/invocations/\")`\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: 会话头设置\n142: \n143: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 已初始化，`session_id` 为 `\"abc123\"`\n144: - **WHEN** 发送任意 HTTP 请求\n145: - **THEN** 请求 SHALL 包含 header `x-agentcube-session-id: abc123`\n146: \n147: #### Scenario: 执行命令请求\n148: \n149: - **GIVEN** 调用 `execute_command(\"ls -la\", timeout=30)`\n150: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n151: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `POST {base_url}api/execute`\n152: - **AND** body 为 JSON `{\"command\": [\"ls\", \"-la\"], \"timeout\": \"30s\"}`\n153: - **AND** read timeout 为 `30 + 2.0 = 32.0` 秒（缓冲 2 秒避免 ReadTimeout）\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 字符串转数组\n156: \n157: - **GIVEN** 调用 `execute_command(\"ls -la\")` (字符串参数)\n158: - **WHEN** 构造请求 body\n159: - **THEN** `command` SHALL 被转换为 `[\"ls\", \"-la\"]`\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 数组参数\n162: \n163: - **GIVEN** 调用 `execute_command([\"ls\", \"-la\"])` (数组参数)\n164: - **WHEN** 构造请求 body\n165: - **THEN** `command` SHALL 直接使用 `[\"ls\", \"-la\"]`\n166: \n167: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 默认超时\n168: \n169: - **GIVEN** 调用 `execute_command(\"ls\")` 未指定 timeout\n170: - **AND** 客户端默认 `timeout=120`\n171: - **WHEN** 构造请求\n172: - **THEN** body 中 `timeout` SHALL 为 `\"120s\"`\n173: - **AND** read timeout SHALL 为 `120 + 2.0 = 122.0` 秒\n174: \n175: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 非零退出码\n176: \n177: - **GIVEN** 远程命令返回 JSON `{\"exit_code\": 1, \"stderr\": \"error output\", \"stdout\": \"\"}`\n178: - **WHEN** 解析响应\n179: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 抛出 `CommandExecutionError`，包含 `exit_code=1`, `stderr=\"error output\"`, `command`\n180: \n181: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 成功\n182: \n183: - **GIVEN** 远程命令返回 JSON `{\"exit_code\": 0, \"stdout\": \"file1\\nfile2\", \"stderr\": \"\"}`\n184: - **WHEN** 解析响应\n185: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 返回 `\"file1\\nfile2\"`\n186: \n187: #### Scenario: 写文件请求\n188: \n189: - **GIVEN** 调用 `write_file(\"hello world\", \"/tmp/test.txt\")`\n190: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n191: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `POST {base_url}api/files`\n192: - **AND** body 为 JSON `{\"path\": \"/tmp/test.txt\", \"content\": \"aGVsbG8gd29ybGQ=\" (base64), \"mode\": \"0644\"}`\n193: - **AND** header `Content-Type: application/json`\n194: \n195: #### Scenario: 写文件 - base64 编码\n196: \n197: - **GIVEN** `content` 为 UTF-8 字符串\n198: - **WHEN** 构造请求 body\n199: - **THEN** `content` SHALL 先编码为 UTF-8 字节，再 base64 编码为字符串\n200: \n201: #### Scenario: 上传文件请求\n202: \n203: - **GIVEN** 调用 `upload_file(\"/local/file.txt\", \"/remote/file.txt\")`\n204: - **AND** 本地文件存在\n205: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n206: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `POST {base_url}api/files` (multipart/form-data)\n207: - **AND** 包含 `files={'file': <file content>}`\n208: - **AND** 包含 `data={'path': '/remote/file.txt', 'mode': '0644'}`\n209: - **AND** header 包含 `x-agentcube-session-id`\n210: - **AND** 不设置 JSON Content-Type（因为是 multipart）\n211: \n212: #### Scenario: 上传文件 - 文件不存在\n213: \n214: - **GIVEN** 本地文件 `/nonexistent/file.txt` 不存在\n215: - **WHEN** 调用 `upload_file(\"/nonexistent/file.txt\", \"/remote/file.txt\")`\n216: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 抛出 `FileNotFoundError`\n217: \n218: #### Scenario: 下载文件请求\n219: \n220: - **GIVEN** 调用 `download_file(\"/remote/file.txt\", \"/local/file.txt\")`\n221: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n222: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `GET {base_url}api/files/remote/file.txt` (去除前导 `/`)\n223: - **AND** 设置 `stream=True`\n224: - **AND** 将响应内容写入本地路径 `/local/file.txt`\n225: \n226: #### Scenario: 下载文件 - 创建父目录\n227: \n228: - **GIVEN** 调用 `download_file(\"/remote/file.txt\", \"/local/subdir/file.txt\")`\n229: - **AND** `/local/subdir/` 目录不存在\n230: - **WHEN** 写入文件\n231: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 创建父目录 `/local/subdir/`\n232: \n233: #### Scenario: 列出文件请求\n234: \n235: - **GIVEN** 调用 `list_files(\"/home\")`\n236: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n237: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `GET {base_url}api/files` 并带上 query 参数 `path=/home`\n238: \n239: #### Scenario: 列出文件 - 默认路径\n240: \n241: - **GIVEN** 调用 `list_files()` 未传入参数\n242: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n243: - **THEN** query 参数 `path` SHALL 默认为 `\".\"`\n244: \n245: #### Scenario: Close 方法\n246: \n247: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 有活跃的 HTTP session\n248: - **WHEN** 调用 `client.close()`\n249: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 关闭底层的 `requests.Session`\n250: \n251: ---\n252: \n253: ### Requirement: Agent Runtime Data Plane HTTP 客户端\n254: \n255: 系统应实现 `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 支持通过 Router 调用 Agent Runtime。\n256: \n257: #### Scenario: Base URL 构建\n258: \n259: - **GIVEN** 构造时传入 `router_url=\"https://router.example.com\"`, `namespace=\"prod\"`, `agent_name=\"my-agent\"`\n260: - **WHEN** 初始化客户端\n261: - **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL 为 `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/prod/agent-runtimes/my-agent/invocations/\")`\n262: \n263: #### Scenario: Bootstrap Session ID - 成功\n264: \n265: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 初始化完成\n266: - **WHEN** 调用 `bootstrap_session_id()`\n267: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `GET {base_url}` (无额外路径)\n268: - **AND** 从响应 header `x-agentcube-session-id` 获取并返回 session id\n269: \n270: #### Scenario: Bootstrap Session ID - 缺失 header\n271: \n272: - **GIVEN** bootstrap `GET` 请求成功但响应 header 中没有 `x-agentcube-session-id`\n273: - **WHEN** 尝试提取 session id\n274: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 抛出 `ValueError(\"Missing required response header: x-agentcube-session-id\")`\n275: \n276: #### Scenario: Invoke 请求\n277: \n278: - **GIVEN** `session_id` 为 `\"sess-123\"`\n279: - **WHEN** 调用 `invoke(session_id, {\"input\": \"test\"}, timeout=60)`\n280: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `POST {base_url}`\n281: - **AND** headers 包含 `x-agentcube-session-id: sess-123`\n282: - **AND** headers 包含 `Content-Type: application/json`\n283: - **AND** body 为 JSON `{\"input\": \"test\"}`\n284: - **AND** 超时为 `(connect_timeout, 60)` 默认 `(5.0, 60)`\n285: \n286: #### Scenario: Invoke 无 session_id\n287: \n288: - **GIVEN** `session_id` 为 `None` 或空字符串\n289: - **WHEN** 调用 `invoke(session_id, payload)`\n290: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 抛出 `ValueError(\"AgentRuntime session_id is not initialized\")`\n291: \n292: #### Scenario: Invoke 返回 Response 对象\n293: \n294: - **GIVEN** `invoke` 请求成功\n295: - **WHEN** 函数返回\n296: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 返回 `requests.Response` 对象（由调用方解析 JSON）\n297: \n298: #### Scenario: Session Header 常量\n299: \n300: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 类定义\n301: - **WHEN** 检查类属性\n302: - **THEN** `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"` SHALL 定义为类常量\n303: \n304: #### Scenario: Close 方法\n305: \n306: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 有活跃的 HTTP session\n307: - **WHEN** 调用 `client.close()`\n308: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 关闭底层的 `requests.Session`\n309: \n310: ---\n311: \n312: ### Requirement: 超时配置统一\n313: \n314: 系统应支持统一的超时配置，默认读超时 120 秒，连接超时 5 秒。\n315: \n316: #### Scenario: Control Plane 默认超时\n317: \n318: - **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` 使用默认参数构造\n319: - **WHEN** 发送任意请求\n320: - **THEN** 超时 SHALL 为 `(5.0, 120)` (connect_timeout, read_timeout)\n321: \n322: #### Scenario: Code Interpreter Data Plane 默认超时\n323: \n324: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 使用默认参数构造\n325: - **WHEN** 发送任意请求\n326: - **THEN** 默认 `timeout` SHALL 为 `120`，`connect_timeout` SHALL 为 `5.0`\n327: \n328: #### Scenario: Agent Runtime Data Plane 默认超时\n329: \n330: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 使用默认参数构造\n331: - **WHEN** 发送任意请求\n332: - **THEN** 默认 `timeout` SHALL 为 `120`，`connect_timeout` SHALL 为 `5.0`\n333: \n334: #### Scenario: 自定义超时\n335: \n336: - **GIVEN** 构造 `ControlPlaneClient(timeout=60, connect_timeout=3.0)`\n337: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n338: - **THEN** 超时 SHALL 为 `(3.0, 60)`\n339: \n340: #### Scenario: Per-call 超时覆盖 - execute_command\n341: \n342: - **GIVEN** `execute_command(command, timeout=30)`\n343: - **WHEN** 该调用执行\n344: - **THEN** read timeout SHALL 使用 `30`（加缓冲 2 秒后为 32），connect timeout 使用实例默认值\n345: \n346: #### Scenario: Per-call 超时覆盖 - invoke\n347: \n348: - **GIVEN** `invoke(..., timeout=30.0)`\n349: - **WHEN** 该调用执行\n350: - **THEN** read timeout SHALL 使用 `30.0`，connect timeout 使用实例默认值\n351: \n352: ---\n353: \n354: ### Requirement: 异常层次结构\n355: \n356: 系统应定义清晰的异常类层次，便于调用方捕获和处理错误。\n357: \n358: #### Scenario: 异常继承\n359: \n360: - **GIVEN** 异常类定义在 `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n361: - **WHEN** 检查类层次\n362: - **THEN** `AgentCubeError` SHALL 继承 `Exception`\n363: - **AND** `CommandExecutionError` SHALL 继承 `AgentCubeError`\n364: - **AND** `SessionError` SHALL 继承 `AgentCubeError`\n365: - **AND** `DataPlaneError` SHALL 继承 `AgentCubeError`\n366: \n367: #### Scenario: CommandExecutionError 构造\n368: \n369: - **GIVEN** 远程命令执行失败，退出码为 2，stderr 为 \"failed\"，命令为 \"ls -la\"\n370: - **WHEN** 构造 `CommandExecutionError(2, \"failed\", \"ls -la\")`\n371: - **THEN** 异常 SHALL 包含属性 `exit_code=2`, `stderr=\"failed\"`, `command=\"ls -la\"`\n372: - **AND** 异常消息 SHALL 为 `\"Command failed (exit 2): failed\"`\n373: \n374: #### Scenario: CommandExecutionError 默认 command\n375: \n376: - **GIVEN** 构造 `CommandExecutionError(1, \"error\")` 不传入 command\n377: - **WHEN** 异常创建\n378: - **THEN** `command` 属性 SHALL 为 `None`\n379: \n380: #### Scenario: SessionError 基类\n381: \n382: - **GIVEN** `SessionError` 定义\n383: - **WHEN** 检查类定义\n384: - **THEN** `SessionError` SHALL 为 `AgentCubeError` 的子类，文档字符串为 \"Raised when session creation or management fails\"\n385: \n386: #### Scenario: DataPlaneError 基类\n387: \n388: - **GIVEN** `DataPlaneError` 定义\n389: - **WHEN** 检查类定义\n390: - **THEN** `DataPlaneError` SHALL 为 `AgentCubeError` 的子类，文档字符串为 \"Raised when Data Plane operations fail\"\n391: \n392: ---\n393: \n394: ### Requirement: Token 文件读取\n395: \n396: 系统应支持从文件读取认证 token，处理文件不存在情况。\n397: \n398: #### Scenario: 读取 token 文件成功\n399: \n400: - **GIVEN** 文件 `/path/to/token` 内容为 `\"my-secret-token\\n\"`\n401: - **WHEN** 调用 `read_token_from_file(\"/path/to/token\")`\n402: - **THEN** 返回 `\"my-secret-token\"` (已 strip)\n403: \n404: #### Scenario: 读取 token 文件 - 多行\n405: \n406: - **GIVEN** 文件内容为 `\"token-line1\\ntoken-line2\\n\"`\n407: - **WHEN** 调用 `read_token_from_file`\n408: - **THEN** 返回 `\"token-line1\\ntoken-line2\"` (仅 strip 前后空白)\n409: \n410: #### Scenario: 文件不存在\n411: \n412: - **GIVEN** 文件 `/nonexistent/token` 不存在\n413: - **WHEN** 调用 `read_token_from_file(\"/nonexistent/token\")`\n414: - **THEN** 返回空字符串 `\"\"` (不抛出异常)\n415: \n416: #### Scenario: 文件读取权限错误\n417: \n418: - **GIVEN** 文件存在但无读取权限\n419: - **WHEN** 调用 `read_token_from_file`\n420: - **THEN** 异常 SHALL 向上传播（不捕获）\n421: \n422: ---\n423: \n424: ### Requirement: 日志工具\n425: \n426: 系统应提供日志工具函数。\n427: \n428: #### Scenario: Logger 创建\n429: \n430: - **GIVEN** 调用 `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\")`\n431: - **WHEN** 函数返回\n432: - **THEN** 返回一个 `logging.Logger` 实例，名称为 `\"agentcube.client\"`\n433: \n434: #### Scenario: 默认日志级别\n435: \n436: - **GIVEN** 调用 `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\")` 不传入 level\n437: - **WHEN** 创建 logger\n438: - **THEN** 日志级别 SHALL 默认为 `logging.INFO`\n439: \n440: #### Scenario: 自定义日志级别\n441: \n442: - **GIVEN** 调用 `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\", level=logging.DEBUG)`\n443: - **WHEN** 创建 logger\n444: - **THEN** 日志级别 SHALL 为 `logging.DEBUG`\n445: \n446: #### Scenario: 字符串日志级别\n447: \n448: - **GIVEN** 调用 `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\", level=\"DEBUG\")`\n449: - **WHEN** 创建 logger\n450: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 将字符串 `\"DEBUG\"` 转换为 `logging.DEBUG`\n451: \n452: ---\n453: \n454: ### Requirement: 公共 API 导出\n455: \n456: 系统应从包根导出公共类。\n457: \n458: #### Scenario: 根包导出\n459: \n460: - **GIVEN** `from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient`\n461: - **WHEN** 执行导入\n462: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterClient` 和 `AgentRuntimeClient` SHALL 可用\n463: \n464: #### Scenario: clients 子包导出\n465: \n466: - **GIVEN** `from agentcube.clients import ControlPlaneClient, CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient, AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n467: - **WHEN** 执行导入\n468: - **THEN** 三个类 SHALL 可用\n469: \n470: #### Scenario: __all__ 定义\n471: \n472: - **GIVEN** `agentcube/__init__.py` 文件\n473: - **WHEN** 检查 `__all__`\n474: - **THEN** `__all__` SHALL 包含 `[\"CodeInterpreterClient\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\"]`\n475: \n476: #### Scenario: clients __all__ 定义\n477: \n478: - **GIVEN** `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` 文件\n479: - **WHEN** 检查 `__all__`\n480: - **THEN** `__all__` SHALL 包含 `[\"ControlPlaneClient\", \"CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\", \"AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\"]`\n481: \n482: ---\n483: \n484: ## Implementation Files\n485: \n486: | File | Purpose |\n487: |------|---------|\n488: | `agentcube/utils/http.py` | `create_session` 函数 |\n489: | `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | `read_token_from_file` 函数 |\n490: | `agentcube/utils/log.py` | `get_logger` 函数 |\n491: | `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` | 工具模块标记 |\n492: | `agentcube/exceptions.py` | 异常类定义 |\n493: | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` 类 |\n494: | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 类 |\n495: | `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 类 |\n496: | `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | 客户端导出 |\n497: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | 包根导出 |\n498: \n499: ---\n500: \n501: ## Dependencies\n502: \n503: | Package | Purpose |\n504: |---------|---------|\n505: | `requests` | HTTP 客户端 |\n506: | `PyJWT>=2.0.0` | JWT 处理（如需要） |\n507: | `cryptography` | 加密支持（如需要） |\n508: \n509: ---\n510: \n511: ## Validation Checklist\n512: \n513: - [ ] `create_session()` 创建带 `HTTPAdapter` 的 `requests.Session`\n514: - [ ] `create_session()` 支持自定义 `pool_connections` 和 `pool_maxsize`\n515: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.create_session` POST 正确 JSON body 并返回 `sessionId`\n516: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.delete_session` 对 404 返回 `True`\n517: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient` 从 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 读取 base_url\n518: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient` 从参数或文件读取 auth_token\n519: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.close()` 关闭 session\n520: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 正确构建 base_url\n521: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 设置 `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n522: - [ ] `execute_command` 正确构造请求 body 和超时\n523: - [ ] `execute_command` 对非零退出码抛出 `CommandExecutionError`\n524: - [ ] `write_file` base64 编码 content\n525: - [ ] `upload_file` 使用 multipart/form-data\n526: - [ ] `download_file` 使用 `stream=True`\n527: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id` 提取 header\n528: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke` 正确设置 headers\n529: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.SESSION_HEADER` 常量\n530: - [ ] 超时默认值 `(connect_timeout=5.0, timeout=120)`\n531: - [ ] 异常类层次正确\n532: - [ ] `CommandExecutionError` 包含 `exit_code`, `stderr`, `command`\n533: - [ ] `read_token_from_file` 对不存在文件返回空字符串\n534: - [ ] `get_logger` 返回正确命名的 logger\n535: - [ ] 公共 API 从 `agentcube` 和 `agentcube.clients` 正确导出\n\n(End of file - total 535 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Specification: AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube Python SDK 实现统一的 HTTP 客户端基础设施，支持控制面和数据面的 HTTP 通信，包括连接池管理、超时配置、会话管理和错误处理。\n\n---\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: HTTP Session 创建与连接池\n\n系统应使用 `requests.Session` 配合 `HTTPAdapter` 实现连接池复用，支持自定义连接池大小。\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775889027510,"end":1775889027535}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775889027542,"sessionID":"ses_284c439adffe9RjKJYXKdSj8yG","part":{"id":"prt_d7b3c0df9001WNiPWIe8Z2H2BN","messageID":"msg_d7b3be32a001DA2dvSOi948F21","sessionID":"ses_284c439adffe9RjKJYXKdSj8yG","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-709b4e361c7e4aec8695e08ec825fa50","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/ci-cd/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/ci-cd/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # CI/CD Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: Automate validation on pull requests (build, lint, tests, codegen drift checks), publish container images on pushes to `main` and version tags, run end-to-end tests on Kind, exercise the Python SDK, and enforce spelling and copyright consistency.\n5: \n6: ## Requirements\n7: \n8: ### Requirement: Pull request build verification\n9: The system SHALL build the Workload Manager Docker image on pull requests targeting `main` or `release-*` branches.\n10: \n11: #### Scenario: Docker build in CI\n12: - **GIVEN** a pull request to `main` or `release-*`\n13: - **WHEN** the “Agentcube CI Workflow” job runs\n14: - **THEN** it SHALL checkout the repository, set up Docker Buildx, verify `docker`/`buildx` versions, and run `make docker-build`\n15: \n16: ### Requirement: Go lint on changed Go code\n17: The system SHALL run `make lint` (golangci-lint) when Go-related paths change on pull requests to `main` or `release-*`.\n18: \n19: #### Scenario: Path-filtered lint\n20: - **GIVEN** a pull request and path filter matches `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, or `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n21: - **WHEN** the Lint workflow runs\n22: - **THEN** it SHALL use Go `1.24` and execute `make lint`\n23: \n24: ### Requirement: Code generation check\n25: The system SHALL verify generated artifacts match `make gen-all` when API, hack, workflow, or Makefile inputs change.\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: Regenerate and diff\n28: - **GIVEN** path filter matches `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, or `Makefile`\n29: - **WHEN** the Codegen Check workflow runs with Go `1.24.4`\n30: - **THEN** it SHALL run `make gen-check` (which runs `gen-all` and `git diff --exit-code`)\n31: \n32: ### Requirement: Go test coverage reporting\n33: The system SHALL run race-enabled coverage tests on `pkg/...` for qualifying pull requests and merge groups, optionally uploading to Codecov.\n34: \n35: #### Scenario: Coverage command\n36: - **GIVEN** path filter `coverage` matches (broad glob excluding some media/docs per workflow)\n37: - **WHEN** the Test Coverage job runs with Go `1.24`\n38: - **THEN** it SHALL execute `go test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...` and upload `coverage.out` as an artifact\n39: \n40: ### Requirement: E2E testing on Kind\n41: The system SHALL run `make e2e` in CI using a Kind-capable Ubuntu runner, capturing logs on failure.\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: E2E job lifecycle\n44: - **GIVEN** a pull request to `main` or `release-*`\n45: - **WHEN** the E2E workflow runs\n46: - **THEN** it SHALL set `ARTIFACTS_PATH=${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`, install Kind tool `v0.30.0` (`install_only: true`), run `make e2e` with Go `1.23`, upload `e2e-logs` on failure, and always run `make e2e-clean`\n47: \n48: ### Requirement: Python SDK unit tests\n49: The system SHALL run pytest for the SDK when `sdk-python/**` changes.\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: Editable install and pytest\n52: - **GIVEN** path filter matches `sdk-python/**`\n53: - **WHEN** the Python SDK Tests job runs with Python `3.12` in `sdk-python/`\n54: - **THEN** it SHALL `pip install pytest`, `pip install -e .`, and run `python -m pytest tests/ -v`\n55: \n56: ### Requirement: Python lint\n57: The system SHALL run Ruff from repository root using `pyproject.toml` when Python-touching paths change.\n58: \n59: #### Scenario: Ruff check\n60: - **GIVEN** path filter matches `cmd/cli/**`, `sdk-python/**`, `example/**`, `test/**/*.py`, `pyproject.toml`, or the workflow file\n61: - **WHEN** the Python Lint job runs with Python `3.10`\n62: - **THEN** it SHALL `pip install ruff` and run `python3 -m ruff check . --config pyproject.toml`\n63: \n64: ### Requirement: Spelling check (codespell)\n65: The system SHALL run codespell on the repository for pull requests to `main` or `release-*`, temporarily moving files that cause false positives.\n66: \n67: #### Scenario: Codespell invocation\n68: - **GIVEN** checkout complete\n69: - **WHEN** codespell runs after backup/remove of `pyproject.toml`, `package-lock.json`, `package.json` at repo root (and nested copies per `find`)\n70: - **THEN** it SHALL use `pip install codespell` and run codespell with `--check-filenames`, specified `--skip` globs, and `--ignore-words-list fo,nam,te,notin,NotIn` on `.`, then restore backed-up files\n71: \n72: ### Requirement: Copyright header check\n73: The system SHALL ensure `make gen-copyright` produces no git diff when applicable files change.\n74: \n75: #### Scenario: Copyright workflow\n76: - **GIVEN** path filter marks `copyright` (all paths minus exclusions for md/svg/png/docs/.github per workflow)\n77: - **WHEN** the job runs\n78: - **THEN** it SHALL install `moreutils` (`sponge`), run `make gen-copyright`, and `git diff --exit-code`\n79: \n80: ### Requirement: Release image publication\n81: The system SHALL build and push multi-architecture images for workloadmanager, router, and picod to GitHub Container Registry on pushes to `main` and on semantic version tags.\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Tag selects image tag\n84: - **GIVEN** a `push` event\n85: - **WHEN** `github.ref_type` is `tag`, environment `TAG` SHALL be `github.ref_name`; otherwise `TAG` SHALL be `latest`\n86: - **THEN** the job SHALL log in to `ghcr.io` with `GITHUB_TOKEN` and run `make docker-buildx-push*`, setting `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}` and per-image `*_IMAGE=<name>:${TAG}`\n87: \n88: ### Requirement: Workflow approval for first-time contributors\n89: The system SHALL optionally approve pending workflow runs for pull requests from repeat contributors or those labeled `ok-to-test`.\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: Approve action_required runs\n92: - **GIVEN** `pull_request_target` on `main` or `release-**` with label/sync events\n93: - **WHEN** the contributor is not first-time (more than one PR) or PR has `ok-to-test`\n94: - **THEN** the workflow SHALL list workflow runs for the head SHA with `status: action_required` and call `approveWorkflowRun` for each\n\n(End of file - total 94 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# CI/CD Specification\n\n## Purpose\nAutomate validation on pull requests (build, lint, tests, codegen drift checks), publish container images on pushes to `main` and version tags, run end-to-end tests on Kind, exercise the Python SDK, and enforce spelling and copyright consistency.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Pull request build verification\nThe system SHALL build the Workload Manager Docker image on pull requests targeting `main` or `release-*` branches.\n\n#### Scenario: Docker build in CI\n- **GIVEN** a pull request to `main` or `release-*`\n- **WHEN** the “Agentcube CI Workflow” job runs\n- **THEN** it SHALL checkout the repository, set up Docker Buildx, verify `docker`/`buildx` versions, and run `make docker-build`\n\n### Requirement: Go lint on changed Go code\nThe system SHALL run `make lint` (golangci-lint) when Go-related paths change on pull requests to `main` or `release-*`.\n\n#### Scenario: Path-filtered lint\n- **GIVEN** a pull request and path filter matches `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, or `.github/workflows/lint.yml`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/ci-cd/spec.md","time":{"start":1775889027515,"end":1775889027540}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775889027544,"sessionID":"ses_284c439adffe9RjKJYXKdSj8yG","part":{"id":"prt_d7b3c119a001vz8FQlFckap2AK","messageID":"msg_d7b3be32a001DA2dvSOi948F21","sessionID":"ses_284c439adffe9RjKJYXKdSj8yG","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-d399c479dca04d4aa3c08e0d0ad727a6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/ci-cd/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/ci-cd/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube CI/CD — Design\n2: \n3: Sources: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/.github/workflows/`, `/tmp/agentcube-ref/test/`, and (for Make targets) `/tmp/agentcube-ref/Makefile`.\n4: \n5: ## GitHub Actions workflows (summary table)\n6: \n7: | Filename | Workflow `name` | Trigger events | Path filters (dorny/paths-filter or notes) | Jobs | Key steps | Env vars (job/step) | Secrets |\n8: |----------|-----------------|----------------|---------------------------------------------|------|-----------|---------------------|---------|\n9: | `main.yml` | Agentcube CI Workflow | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `build` | Checkout; Docker Buildx setup; verify Docker; `make docker-build` | — | — |\n10: | `e2e.yml` | Agentcube E2E Tests | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `e2e-test` | Checkout; Go 1.23; `helm/kind-action@v1` **install_only** Kind v0.30.0, `cluster_name: agentcube-e2e`; `export ARTIFACTS_PATH=${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`; `make e2e`; on failure upload `e2e-logs/`; `always` → `make e2e-clean` | `ARTIFACTS_PATH` (shell) | — |\n11: | `lint.yml` | Lint | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `lint`: `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, `.github/workflows/lint.yml` | `golangci` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Go 1.24; `make lint` | — | — |\n12: | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | Python SDK Tests | `pull_request`, `merge_group` | `sdk`: `sdk-python/**` | `python-sdk-tests` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Python 3.12 in `sdk-python/`; `pip install pytest`; `pip install -e .`; `python -m pytest tests/ -v` | Default `working-directory: sdk-python` | — |\n13: | `python-lint.yml` | Python Lint | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `python`: `cmd/cli/**`, `sdk-python/**`, `example/**`, `test/**/*.py`, `pyproject.toml`, workflow self | `python_lint` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Python 3.10; `pip install ruff`; `ruff check . --config pyproject.toml` | — | — |\n14: | `test-coverage.yml` | Test Coverage | `pull_request`, `merge_group`, `workflow_call` | `coverage`: `**` minus `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png` | `coverage` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: free disk space; Go 1.24; `go test` with coverage; step summary; Codecov upload; artifact `go-coverage` | `CODECOV_TOKEN` passed to Codecov action when present | `secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN` (optional; declared for `workflow_call`) |\n15: | `codegen-check.yml` | Codegen Check | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `codegen`: `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, `Makefile` | `codegen-check` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Go 1.24.4; `make gen-check` | — | — |\n16: | `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright Check | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `copyright`: all files except `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`, `.github/**` | `build` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: `apt install moreutils`; `make gen-copyright`; `git diff --exit-code` | — | — |\n17: | `codespell.yml` | Codespell | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none — scans tree after temporarily removing some manifests)* | `codespell` | Backup/remove `pyproject.toml`, `package.json`, `package-lock.json`; `pip install codespell`; `codespell` with `--check-filenames`, `--skip`, `--ignore-words-list`; restore files | — | — |\n18: | `build-push-release.yml` | Build and Push Release Images | `push` → `main`; `push` tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*` | *(none)* | `build-and-push` | Checkout; Go 1.24.4; Buildx; `docker/login-action` to `ghcr.io`; set `TAG` from ref; `make docker-buildx-push` (workload manager), `docker-buildx-push-router`, `docker-buildx-push-picod` with `IMAGE_REGISTRY` | `TAG`, `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}` | `GITHUB_TOKEN` (registry login) |\n19: | `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Dify Plugin Publish | `push` tags `dify-plugin/v*` | *(none)* | `publish` | Download `dify-plugin` CLI 0.0.6; install `yq`; read `manifest.yaml`; package plugin; checkout `author/dify-plugins` with token; move `.difypkg`; branch, commit, push; `gh pr create` to `langgenius/dify-plugins` | `GH_TOKEN` on PR step | `PLUGIN_ACTION` (repo checkout + `gh`; cross-repo PR) |\n20: | `workflows-approve.yml` | Approve Workflows | `pull_request_target` types `labeled`, `synchronize` → `main`, `release-**` | *(logic: first-time contributor vs `ok-to-test` label)* | `approve` | `github-script`: list contributor PRs; if not first-time or has `ok-to-test`, list `action_required` workflow runs for SHA and approve | — | `GITHUB_TOKEN` |\n21: \n22: ### Workflow notes\n23: \n24: - **`e2e.yml`**: Uses Kind action with `install_only: true` so the cluster is created by `run_e2e.sh` (`kind create cluster`), avoiding double-creation.\n25: - **`test-coverage.yml`**: `workflow_call` declares `CODECOV_TOKEN` optional for reusable invocation; PR runs use the repo secret when configured.\n26: - **`build-push-release.yml`**: Uses older action major versions (`checkout@v3`, `setup-go@v4`, `buildx@v2`) than most other workflows.\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## E2E test setup (`test/e2e/run_e2e.sh`)\n31: \n32: ### Kind cluster\n33: \n34: | Item | Value / behavior |\n35: |------|------------------|\n36: | Default cluster name | `E2E_CLUSTER_NAME` → `agentcube-e2e` |\n37: | Creation | `kind create cluster --name \"${E2E_CLUSTER_NAME}\"` if missing; if exists and `E2E_CLEAN_CLUSTER=true` (default), delete then recreate |\n38: | CI alignment | `.github/workflows/e2e.yml` installs Kind **v0.30.0** via `helm/kind-action@v1` (`install_only: true`) |\n39: | Skip setup | `E2E_SKIP_SETUP=true` skips `run_setup` and assumes an existing cluster |\n40: \n41: ### CRD / agent-sandbox installation\n42: \n43: Applied via `kubectl apply --validate=false` after downloading release assets (URLs built from `AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION`, default **`v0.1.1`**):\n44: \n45: 1. `https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/download/${AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION}/manifest.yaml`\n46: 2. `https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/download/${AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION}/extensions.yaml`\n47: \n48: ### Images pre-pulled and loaded into Kind\n49: \n50: - `registry.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/agent-sandbox-controller:${AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION}`\n51: - `python:3.9-slim` (echo agent workload)\n52: \n53: Local images built and loaded:\n54: \n55: - `make docker-build` → default `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE` **`workloadmanager:latest`**\n56: - `make docker-build-router` → **`agentcube-router:latest`**\n57: - `make docker-build-picod` → **`picod:latest`**\n58: - `REDIS_IMAGE` default **`redis:7-alpine`** (Deployment + Service in namespace)\n59: \n60: ### Helm (AgentCube chart)\n61: \n62: | Item | Value |\n63: |------|--------|\n64: | Chart path | `manifests/charts/base` |\n65: | Release / namespace | `agentcube` in `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` (default `agentcube`), `--create-namespace` |\n66: | Redis addr | `redis.${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}.svc.cluster.local:6379`, password empty |\n67: | Workload manager image | `repository=workloadmanager`, `tag=latest` |\n68: | Router image | `repository=agentcube-router`, `tag=latest` |\n69: | Router RBAC | `router.rbac.create=true`, `router.serviceAccountName=agentcube-router` |\n70: | Extra env (JSON via `--set-json`) | Workload manager: `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`, `JWT_KEY_SECRET_NAMESPACE=agentcube`; Router: `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false` |\n71: | Wait | `helm upgrade --install ... --wait` |\n72: \n73: ### Kubernetes fixtures applied during setup\n74: \n75: | Path | Purpose |\n76: |------|---------|\n77: | `test/e2e/echo_agent.yaml` | `AgentRuntime` `echo-agent` in `agentcube` |\n78: | Generated from `echo_agent.yaml` (sed) | `echo-agent-short-ttl` with `sessionTimeout: \"30s\"` for TTL tests |\n79: | `test/e2e/e2e_code_interpreter.yaml` | `CodeInterpreter` `e2e-code-interpreter` in `agentcube` |\n80: \n81: Warm-pool Go tests apply `e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml` at runtime (not in initial `kubectl apply` list in the shell script).\n82: \n83: ### Port forwards and health checks\n84: \n85: - Workload manager: `kubectl port-forward svc/workloadmanager` → `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT` (default **8080**) → pod 8080\n86: - Router: `kubectl port-forward svc/agentcube-router` → `ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT` (default **8081**) → pod 8080\n87: - Readiness: `curl` to `http://localhost:${WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT}/health` and `http://localhost:${ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT}/health/live`\n88: \n89: ### Auth for tests\n90: \n91: - ServiceAccount `e2e-test` in `agentcube` + `ClusterRoleBinding` to `workloadmanager` clusterrole\n92: - API token: `kubectl create token e2e-test -n agentcube --duration=24h` → `API_TOKEN`\n93: \n94: ### Python venv for E2E\n95: \n96: - Directory: `E2E_VENV_DIR` (default `/tmp/agentcube-e2e-venv`)\n97: - `python3 -m venv`, `pip install -e ./sdk-python`, verify `import agentcube`\n98: \n99: ### Test commands invoked by `run_e2e.sh`\n100: \n101: **Go** (from repository root):\n102: \n103: ```bash\n104: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=\"http://localhost:${WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT}\" \\\n105: ROUTER_URL=\"http://localhost:${ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT}\" \\\n106: API_TOKEN=$API_TOKEN \\\n107: go test -v ./test/e2e/...\n108: ```\n109: \n110: **Python** (after `cd` to `test/e2e`):\n111: \n112: ```bash\n113: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=\"...\" ROUTER_URL=\"...\" API_TOKEN=$API_TOKEN \\\n114: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE=\"${AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE}\" \\\n115: \"$E2E_VENV_DIR/bin/python\" test_codeinterpreter.py\n116: ```\n117: \n118: (`test_codeinterpreter.py` uses `unittest.main()` and appends `--verbose` if missing.)\n119: \n120: ### Failure artifacts\n121: \n122: On test failure, `collect_component_logs` writes under `ARTIFACTS_PATH` (CI: `${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`): workload manager, router, and sandbox pod logs/describes.\n123: \n124: ---\n125: \n126: ## Test directory structure\n127: \n128: ```\n129: test/\n130: ├── OWNERS\n131: └── e2e/\n132:     ├── README.md\n133:     ├── __init__.py\n134:     ├── run_e2e.sh\n135:     ├── e2e_test.go\n136:     ├── test_codeinterpreter.py\n137:     ├── echo_agent.yaml\n138:     ├── e2e_code_interpreter.yaml\n139:     └── e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml\n140: ```\n141: \n142: ### Fixture paths (relative to repo root unless noted)\n143: \n144: | Fixture | Description |\n145: |---------|-------------|\n146: | `test/e2e/echo_agent.yaml` | Echo `AgentRuntime` for router invocation tests |\n147: | `test/e2e/e2e_code_interpreter.yaml` | Standard `CodeInterpreter` (`e2e-code-interpreter`, namespace `agentcube`) |\n148: | `test/e2e/e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml` | `CodeInterpreter` with `warmPoolSize: 2` in `default` (loaded by Go tests from **package cwd** as `e2e_code_interpreter_warmpool.yaml`) |\n149: \n150: ---\n151: \n152: ## Go test commands and flags in CI\n153: \n154: | Workflow / entrypoint | Command | Flags / notes |\n155: |------------------------|---------|----------------|\n156: | `test-coverage.yml` | `go test` | `-race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...` |\n157: | `e2e.yml` via `make e2e` → `run_e2e.sh` | `go test` | `-v ./test/e2e/...` with env `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`, `ROUTER_URL`, `API_TOKEN` |\n158: \n159: ---\n160: \n161: ## Python test commands in CI\n162: \n163: | Workflow | Working dir | Command |\n164: |----------|-------------|---------|\n165: | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | `sdk-python` | `python -m pip install --upgrade pip`; `pip install pytest`; `pip install -e .`; `python -m pytest tests/ -v` |\n166: | `e2e.yml` (via `run_e2e.sh`) | Invoked from `test/e2e/` | `\"$E2E_VENV_DIR/bin/python\" test_codeinterpreter.py` (unittest, verbosity 2) |\n167: \n168: ---\n169: \n170: ## Key Make targets referenced by CI\n171: \n172: | Target | Referenced in | Role |\n173: |--------|----------------|------|\n174: | `docker-build` | `main.yml`, `run_e2e.sh` | Build workload manager image |\n175: | `docker-build-router` | `run_e2e.sh` | Build router image |\n176: | `docker-build-picod` | `run_e2e.sh` | Build picod image |\n177: | `docker-buildx-push` | `build-push-release.yml` | Push workload manager image (`IMAGE_REGISTRY`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE=workloadmanager:${TAG}`) |\n178: | `docker-buildx-push-router` | `build-push-release.yml` | Push router image |\n179: | `docker-buildx-push-picod` | `build-push-release.yml` | Push picod image |\n180: | `e2e` | `e2e.yml` | Run `./test/e2e/run_e2e.sh` |\n181: | `e2e-clean` | `e2e.yml` | `kind delete cluster --name $(E2E_CLUSTER_NAME)`; `rm -rf /tmp/agent-sandbox` |\n182: | `lint` | `lint.yml` | `golangci-lint` (project default) |\n183: | `gen-check` | `codegen-check.yml` | Verify generated code up to date |\n184: | `gen-copyright` | `copyright-check.yml` | Generate copyright headers for check |\n185: \n186: ---\n187: \n188: ## Additional reference: E2E README vs script\n189: \n190: `test/e2e/README.md` states Go **1.24+** and generic “install CRDs and agent-sandbox”; the **CI workflow** pins Go **1.23** for E2E, and **run_e2e.sh** pins **agent-sandbox `v0.1.1`** by default (overridable via `AGENT_SANDBOX_VERSION`).\n\n(End of file - total 190 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube CI/CD — Design\n\nSources: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/.github/workflows/`, `/tmp/agentcube-ref/test/`, and (for Make targets) `/tmp/agentcube-ref/Makefile`.\n\n## GitHub Actions workflows (summary table)\n\n| Filename | Workflow `name` | Trigger events | Path filters (dorny/paths-filter or notes) | Jobs | Key steps | Env vars (job/step) | Secrets |\n|----------|-----------------|----------------|---------------------------------------------|------|-----------|---------------------|---------|\n| `main.yml` | Agentcube CI Workflow | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `build` | Checkout; Docker Buildx setup; verify Docker; `make docker-build` | — | — |\n| `e2e.yml` | Agentcube E2E Tests | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `e2e-test` | Checkout; Go 1.23; `helm/kind-action@v1` **install_only** Kind v0.30.0, `cluster_name: agentcube-e2e`; `export ARTIFACTS_PATH=${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs`; `make e2e`; on failure upload `e2e-logs/`; `always` → `make e2e-clean` | `ARTIFACTS_PATH` (shell) | — |\n| `lint.yml` | Lint | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `lint`: `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, `.github/workflows/lint.yml` | `golangci` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Go 1.24; `make lint` | — | — |\n| `python-sdk-tests.yml` | Python SDK Tests | `pull_request`, `merge_group` | `sdk`: `sdk-python/**` | `python-sdk-tests` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Python 3.12 in `sdk-python/`; `pip install pytest`; `pip install -e .`; `python -m pytest tests/ -v` | Default `working-directory: sdk-python` | — |\n| `python-lint.yml` | Python Lint | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `python`: `cmd/cli/**`, `sdk-python/**`, `example/**`, `test/**/*.py`, `pyproject.toml`, workflow self | `python_lint` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Python 3.10; `pip install ruff`; `ruff check . --config pyproject.toml` | — | — |\n| `test-coverage.yml` | Test Coverage | `pull_request`, `merge_group`, `workflow_call` | `coverage`: `**` minus `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png` | `coverage` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: free disk space; Go 1.24; `go test` with coverage; step summary; Codecov upload; artifact `go-coverage` | `CODECOV_TOKEN` passed to Codecov action when present | `secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN` (optional; declared for `workflow_call`) |\n| `codegen-check.yml` | Codegen Check | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `codegen`: `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, `Makefile` | `codegen-check` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: Go 1.24.4; `make gen-check` | — | — |\n| `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright Check | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | `copyright`: all files except `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`, `.github/**` | `build` | Checkout; paths-filter; if changed: `apt install moreutils`; `make gen-copyright`; `git diff --exit-code` | — | — |\n| `codespell.yml` | Codespell | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none — scans tree after temporarily removing some manifests)* | `codespell` | Backup/remove `pyproject.toml`, `package.json`, `package-lock.json`; `pip install codespell`; `codespell` with `--check-filenames`, `--skip`, `--ignore-words-list`; restore files | — | — |\n| `build-push-release.yml` | Build and Push Release Images | `push` → `main`; `push` tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*` | *(none)* | `build-and-push` | Checkout; Go 1.24.4; Buildx; `docker/login-action` to `ghcr.io`; set `TAG` from ref; `make docker-buildx-push` (workload manager), `docker-buildx-push-router`, `docker-buildx-push-picod` with `IMAGE_REGISTRY` | `TAG`, `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}` | `GITHUB_TOKEN` (registry login) |\n| `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Dify Plugin Publish | `push` tags `dify-plugin/v*` | *(none)* | `publish` | Download `dify-plugin` CLI 0.0.6; install `yq`; read `manifest.yaml`; package plugin; checkout `author/dify-plugins` with token; move `.difypkg`; branch, commit, push; `gh pr create` to `langgenius/dify-plugins` | `GH_TOKEN` on PR step | `PLUGIN_ACTION` (repo checkout + `gh`; cross-repo PR) |\n| `workflows-approve.yml` | Approve Workflows | `pull_request_target` types `labeled`, `synchronize` → `main`, `release-**` | *(logic: first-time contributor vs `ok-to-test` label)* | `approve` | `github-script`: list contributor PRs; if not first-time or has `ok-to-test`, list `action_required` workflow runs for SHA and approve | — | `GITHUB_TOKEN` |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/ci-cd/design.md","time":{"start":1775889027518,"end":1775889027542}}}}
